Model: MoistMix.safetensors
VAE: MoistMix.vae.pt
You could also just specify the VAE to use in cmd line arguments by adding "--vae-path [path to VAE]"

>> Getting empty black images? <<
Add this to your command-line arguments "--no-half-vae"

>>> More useful info <<<
github.com/AUTOMATIC1111/stable-diffusion-webui/wiki
Fyi, Web UI treats safetensor models the same as ckpt, you dont have to rename them or anything to use them, and as the name suggests, they are safer and they load faster.
